bbildungen ausgestattet, sondern jeweils von führenden Spezialisten in anschaulichen Texten beschrieben. Für das Buch wurde die „Methode 9x9“ komplett neu entwickelt und grafisch dargestellt. Autoren: Florian Aicher, Jia Beisi, Adam Caruso, Dietmar Eberle, Franziska Hauser, Vittorio Magnago Lampugnani, Michele Lanza, Arno Lederer, Silvain Malfroy, Adrian Meyer, Marcello Nasso, Fritz Neumeyer, András Pálffy, Miroslav Šik, Laurent Stalder, Eberhard Tröger.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 04. Okt 2022) 7aARCHITECTURE / Study & Teaching.2bisacsh1 aAicher, Florian, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aCaruso, Adam, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aEberle, Dietmar, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aEberle, Dietmar, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aHauser, Franziska, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLampugnani, Magnago, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMalfroy, Silvain, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMeyer, Adrian, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aNasso, Marcello, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aNeumeyer, Fritz, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPálffy, András, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSik, Miroslav, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aStalder, Laurent, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aTröger, Eberhard, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2018 Part 1z978311076248808iTitle is part 